						<div class="postbody">I think even the NES 6502 is good enough for maxing out what the PPU can do, I think you'd need to add more sprites without a scanline limit to need a better CPU to take advantage of anything. Anyone up for making some 2GHZ 6502's with some new 256-sprite no-limit sprites? That'd be amazing, the world needs an epic easy-to-progam 2D PPU, haha.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_rolleyes.gif" alt=":roll:" title="Rolling Eyes" /></div>

